name: "odin"
origin: "sysutils/odin"
version: "0.1.0"
comment: "Minimal service supervisor for FreeBSD-hosted application processes"
maintainer: "petter@hask.no"
www: "https://github.com/glotlabs/odin"
abi: "FreeBSD:*:*"
arch: "freebsd:*"
prefix: "/"
flatsize: 0
desc: <<EOD
odin is a minimal Rust service supervisor for FreeBSD-hosted application
processes. It is intended for long-running third-party applications you own,
not for replacing init, rc.d, or system service management.

This package installs odin under /opt/odin and provides optional FreeBSD
integration files for rc.d and newsyslog.
EOD
